					<h2>Who We Are</h2>
					<img src="/assets/group.jpg" alt=""/>				
					<p>We are group of Dell employees who want to the bring the Right To Education Act to the doorsteps of the needy and underprivileged kids. Our website helps in showing the RTE vacant seats information from class 1 to class 8 of a particular school. Its design is simple and user-friendly. There is a search option provided and any individual can search with area/PIN code/Locality. Once an area is searched, the site lists all the schools available in that area. User can choose a particular school, to get its details and RTE vacant seats.</p>
