				<div class="col_1_of_3 grid_1_of_3">
					<h2>Inspiration</h2>
					<img width="200" src="/assets/Ritik.jpg" alt=""/>
				 	<p>In 2014 March ,we found a cute boy Ritik, an underprivileged kid. He sells panipuri because of economic problems in his family, but he was very much interested in going to school. We spent months in getting RTE information to admit Ritik to a school. We went to each and every school in our nearby locality, to find out the procedure,how to admit him to school under RTE quota. He has the passion to study, but he didn't know how to approach the school. Which ever school we visited ,they told us either seats were full or the time window to apply for admission through RTE was over. So, we admitted him in Modern Angels school, BEML in 3rd Standard. We would admit him to school under RTE in next year. We started this portal to solve the problems we faced while admitting Ritik and to help people like us. </p>
